Palagi kang magiging runner-up ko.

00:40:31.793 --> 00:40:32.592
Maliban sa mga laro.

00:40:34.433 --> 00:40:36.192
"Iyon ang plano." At saka ano?

00:40:37.273 --> 00:40:38.112
